{"tid":1556072,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"經歷左三個月既運動，有少少野想講…希望大家會入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:08:59.000Z","uid":227139,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f05e45f0774b9cc2ba3cf2d92605ab5df91ab0b","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"咁就三個月，自問呢三個月每個星期都有出席唔同運動，當然我唔係最勇敢企最前既人，首先我要向前線<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武</span></span>，中排<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和理非</span></span>，後排<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">物資組</span></span>，仲有其他例如<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣組</span></span>同埋<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所有所有為呢場運動付出過既兄弟姊妹</span></span>講聲<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝你</span></span><br />\n成場運動行到而家一路以黎每一步<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全靠大家一齊努力互相合作</span></span>先會令我地香港人有機會睇到勝利既曙光<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">兄弟姊妹一樣缺一不可</span></span><br />\n呢三個月已經有數不清既手足犧牲既犧牲，被捕既被捕&hellip;更甚既係佢地當中所受到既<span style=\"color: maroon;\">屈辱，被侮，</span>絕對係我地<span style=\"color: maroon;\">難以想像既痛苦</span><br />\n冇錯，我都會有攰既時候，但頭先得閒，我開住youtube，聽返一直以黎巴絲為我地創作既歌曲，mv，我眼淚又再唔受控咁流，男人老狗你地可以笑我眼淺，但係我由細到大冇乜朋友，家底唔好所有野都唔好都試過比人杯，我真係當每一位都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">手足，冇一個係condom！</span></span></strong>我好怕再睇新聞見到你地出事，我好想清算黑警但原諒我真係未有膽量&hellip;<br />\n呢個活動令我地香港年青一輩團結，我地既使命更係為對上對下既幾代而戰，呢場仗，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">一定要贏！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n仲未係休息既時候，攰既時候可以望望身邊每一位，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">不理和勇，互相扶持，共同努力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，加油</span></span><br />\n期待煲底大家相認既一日，我愛你地每一位，愛香港呢個咁美好既地方，<br />\n手足應承我，重整策略，已經冇空間比我地失焦，繼續撐落去為我地居住既地方，為屬於我地既香港打贏呢場仗！<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">願榮光，歸香港</span>"},{"pid":"c9d81608b0c614460f5e2060181b4635b71e33c3","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2ed021f58e52c415b21c7066b3d621c3cba542cc","tid":1556072,"uid":8434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"942d3bf8849a274e000e642b4b545f5b78fe9185","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"希望有人睇到"},{"pid":"7457e43ccf693fdbffd5f4201b5794b728614a37","tid":1556072,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1378c9d418510bb2b661f82db22f7c70742f9d87","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"期待大家除罩相認煲底唱國歌"},{"pid":"f088b9e0d720c447ae08410dc66b48c5da52d42f","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"04426b0f232a497597215c7bc3f3f623a8104d5b","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"e44342d2d2e0d22334174a06fa0f35ea9de27ded","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"6b39a3183600318705592fa3433660b4df098de4","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9bbc5270e65ea166ad5b15d603c597f22bac079d","tid":1556072,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"54795d29714f01550cc31505b7ac44c6bb08f09a","tid":1556072,"u